    "body": "Okay - didn't know this is already implemented.\nI've tested this on `0.20.4` now  - yes, `--touch-events` does work. I get `Invalid --touch-events option: invalid`. But when I execute it with `--touch-devices=invalid` I don't get an error message.\n\nThe function for `--touch-devices` can be found here https://github.com/scheib/chromium/blob/master/ui/events/x/touch_factory_x11.cc#L56.\n"
